A cyberpunk cityscape at night where glowing data streams flow like rivers between a small illuminated workstation in the foreground and towering cloud servers in the distant skyline. The workstation sits on a rooftop garden with potted plants, casting warm amber light, while the massive server towers pulse with electric blue and magenta energy, connected by luminous fiber-optic cables that arc through the rain-slicked air like digital bridges. Holographic database symbols float near the clouds, resembling layered circular discs stacked in formation. The scene captures the intimate scale of local development contrasting with the vast infrastructure of cloud deployment, all rendered in deep teals, hot pinks, and neon oranges reflecting off wet surfaces and glass buildings.
